	This festive and traditional wreath with a twist has a twig heart base decorated with delicious dried fruits including dried whole and sliced oranges and limes, chillies and bay leaves. This wonderful wreath is scented with a spicy Christmas fragrance which can be refilled with our Christmas Mix fragrance oil that creates a wonderful aroma that lingers around the home. This gorgeous twig wreath is then finished with a cream raffia and red ribbon bow and a hanger at the top of the heart. This unusual but very decorative wreath would make the perfect addition to your Christmas decorations hung on your front door, gate, shed or even hung in the window facing the outside. This fantastic dried citrus fruit wreath measures approximately 23cm tall and 24cm wide and is a truly wonderful way to decorate your home during the festive season.</p>
